1 at the next general election or at another time pursuant to
2 this act but not less than twelve (12) months following
3 this bond election. This subsection shall apply only to
4 bond elections held in accordance with this article.
5
6 Section 2. Nothing in this act shall be construed to
7 impact a bond election held prior to July 1, 2025.
8
9 Section 3. This act is effective July 1, 2025.
